1
00:00:26,493 --> 00:00:31,393
片名：海防最前线

2
00:00:42,209 --> 00:00:46,043
有个传说，说海水下住了个人
There's a legend of a man who lives beneath the sea.

3
00:00:46,113 --> 00:00:48,013
他是捞人的
He is a fisher of men,

4
00:00:48,315 --> 00:00:51,978
是落伍者的最后希望
the last hope of all those who have been left behind.

5
00:00:52,052 --> 00:00:55,579
很多逃生者声称，他们感觉到他的手托在自己身下
Many survivors claim to have felt his gripping hands beneath them,

6
00:00:55,655 --> 00:00:57,589
把自己推上了海面
pushing them up to the surface,

7
00:00:57,657 --> 00:01:00,820
低声鼓励他们，直到救援赶来
whispering strength until help could arrive.

8
00:01:00,894 --> 00:01:04,227
但这，当然，只是个传说
But this, of course, is only a legend.

9
00:01:08,168 --> 00:01:09,567
救命
Help!

10
00:01:10,337 --> 00:01:11,702
在这
Over here!

11
00:01:15,909 --> 00:01:17,069
谢蕊琳
Sherilyn!

12
00:01:17,244 --> 00:01:18,268
救命
Help!

13
00:01:18,345 --> 00:01:21,280
夫人，我是海岸警卫队救生员
Ma'am, I'm a Coast Guard rescue swimmer.

14
00:01:21,348 --> 00:01:22,872
我是来救你的
I'm here to help you.

15
00:01:24,151 --> 00:01:28,554
先生，和你的浮标待在一起 我会回来接你的
Sir, stay with your flotation. I'll be back for you.

16
00:01:28,622 --> 00:01:30,681
- 别丢下我  - 待在那
- Don't leave me!  - Just stay there.

17
00:01:30,757 --> 00:01:32,816
别丢下我
Don't you leave me!

18
00:01:36,530 --> 00:01:38,691
救生篮已经在舱外，正在吊下
Basket is outside the cabin door and going down.

19
00:01:38,765 --> 00:01:39,789
收到
Roger. Copy you.

20
00:01:39,866 --> 00:01:42,801
右前方30尺 右前方15尺
Forward and right 30. Forward and right 15.

21
00:01:42,869 --> 00:01:43,858
右前15尺
Right 15.

22
00:01:43,937 --> 00:01:44,926
停，停
Ho, ho, ho!

23
00:01:45,739 --> 00:01:47,900
救生篮入水了
Basket is in the water.

24
00:01:47,974 --> 00:01:49,942
救生员和生还者已经在篮内了
Swimmer and survivor are at the basket.

25
00:01:50,010 --> 00:01:51,875
让你的头先进去
Put your head in first.

26
00:01:55,515 --> 00:01:56,914
我得出去
I gotta get out!

27
00:01:56,983 --> 00:01:58,211
慢点，向前
Easy, forward.

28
00:01:59,052 --> 00:02:01,748
放开，放开
Let go! Let go.

29
00:02:01,988 --> 00:02:04,422
放开，你会淹死她的
Let go. You're drowning her!

30
00:02:09,129 --> 00:02:11,654
救生员给了他脸上一拳
Swimmer just popped him in the face.

31
00:02:15,135 --> 00:02:17,695
他把男人放进篮里了
Okay, he's putting the man in the basket.

32
00:02:17,771 --> 00:02:19,568
男人进篮了
The man is in the basket.

33
00:02:19,873 --> 00:02:21,773
我们要把他拉上来
We're taking the load.

34
00:02:26,546 --> 00:02:27,843
哇，大浪来袭
Whoa, big wave.

35
00:02:33,253 --> 00:02:35,380
出去，出去，你有毛病啊？
Get out! Get out! What's wrong with you?

36
00:02:35,455 --> 00:02:37,116
坐好，闭嘴
Sit there and shut up.

37
00:02:56,977 --> 00:02:58,137
看到救生员了
Swimmer in sight.

38
00:03:02,482 --> 00:03:04,245
准备拉起
Prepare to take the load.

39
00:03:04,317 --> 00:03:06,308
我看到“可以拉起”的信号了
I have the ready-for-pickup signal.

40
00:03:14,761 --> 00:03:17,355
救生员靠近舱门了
Swimmer is approaching cabin door.

41
00:03:17,964 --> 00:03:19,932
生还者看来失去了意识
Survivor looks unconscious.

42
00:03:21,601 --> 00:03:23,694
救生员在舱内了
Swimmer inside the cabin door.

43
00:03:25,839 --> 00:03:28,034
关上舱门
Cabin door closing.

44
00:03:42,289 --> 00:03:43,984
我想你打断了我的鼻子
I think you just broke my nose.

45
00:03:44,057 --> 00:03:46,719
而你可能杀了你太太，先生
And you may have killed your wife, sir.

46
00:03:48,628 --> 00:03:49,959
20分钟到科迪亚克
Twenty minutes to Kodiak.

47
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:52,794
收到，他正在对她进行心肺复苏
Roger. He's giving her CPR.

48
00:03:52,966 --> 00:03:55,662
科迪亚克中心，这是海岸警卫队6096号
Comstate Kodiak, this is Coast Guard 6096.

49
00:03:55,735 --> 00:03:58,363
舱内载有两名低体温生还者
We have two hypothermic survivors onboard.

50
00:03:58,438 --> 00:03:59,462
我们20分钟后到
We'll be there in 20 minutes.

51
00:03:59,539 --> 00:04:02,565
请求派救护车到降落地点
Requesting to have an ambulance on-scene when we land.

52
00:04:22,529 --> 00:04:23,826
哇，搞定了
Whoa, there we go.

53
00:04:25,031 --> 00:04:26,658
- 救活她了？  - 救活她了
Got her?  - Got her!

54
00:04:43,416 --> 00:04:44,974
出发啦，伙计
Attaway, baby.

55
00:04:46,252 --> 00:04:47,651
只有死透了…
There's dead,

56
00:04:50,924 --> 00:04:52,585
才算是死
then there's dead.

57
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,121
我发誓，你年岁越大越棒了
I swear, you get better with age.

58
00:05:23,256 --> 00:05:25,554
- 不得不打他，啊？  - 是啊
- Had to hit him, huh?  - Yeah.

59
00:05:26,159 --> 00:05:28,923
你不是，待在那，待那
You are not. You stay over there! You stay over there!

60
00:05:30,930 --> 00:05:33,990
似乎总是强者失控啊
Seems like it's always the big ones that crack.

61
00:05:36,069 --> 00:05:37,161
中尉
Lieutenant.

62
00:05:37,237 --> 00:05:40,900
组员说她沉到水里了 他们以为你救不活她呢
Crew said that she went under. They thought you'd lost her.

63
00:05:41,307 --> 00:05:43,366
幸运吧我猜
Lucky guess.

64
00:05:44,544 --> 00:05:46,409
幸个屁运
Luck, my ass.

65
00:06:07,967 --> 00:06:10,800
- 我不认为你是来真的  - 你当然不了，本
- I didn't think you were serious.  - Of course you didn't, Ben.

66
00:06:10,870 --> 00:06:12,531
你怎么会认为我来真的呢
How could you possibly think I was serious?

67
00:06:12,605 --> 00:06:14,800
我又不是哪个无名的溺水者
I'm not some nameless drowning victim.

68
00:06:14,874 --> 00:06:18,810
哦，天，我很抱歉 救人和我们的社交有冲突
Oh, gee, I'm sorry saving lives doesn't jive with our social...

69
00:06:20,313 --> 00:06:21,302
那
That's...

70
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:24,576
那是我的椅子
That's my chair.

71
00:06:24,651 --> 00:06:26,710
他说的对，不是那把椅子
Oh, he's right. Not that chair.

72
00:06:27,754 --> 00:06:32,453
对不起，我只是在客厅指了一下 他不知道
I'm sorry. I was just pointing things out in the living room. He didn't know.

73
00:06:33,059 --> 00:06:35,323
我不会拿你的椅子的
I would never take your chair.

74
00:06:42,602 --> 00:06:44,365
搬上去，行吗？
Pick it up, would...

75
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,969
没什么难的，本
Doesn't have to be messy, Ben.

76
00:06:49,042 --> 00:06:52,478
这样简单清楚，对我们双方都是 我们没有孩子
It's clean, simple for both of us. We don't have kids.

77
00:06:55,682 --> 00:06:57,650
那，周五怎么办？
Well, what about Friday?

78
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,417
什么周五怎么办？
What about Friday?

79
00:07:01,488 --> 00:07:03,922
我们要去卡尔和布雷吉特那的
We were gonna go with Carl and Bridget, you know,

80
00:07:03,990 --> 00:07:07,357
那个基地的晚餐舞会
to that dinner-dance thing at the base.

81
00:07:08,928 --> 00:07:11,488
基地？“鸡翅随意吃”？
The base? All-you-can-eat wings?

82
00:07:11,564 --> 00:07:15,159
投飞镖付帐单 这就是我们不能错过的日子？
A dart game to settle the tab? That's the date that we can't break?

83
00:07:15,235 --> 00:07:17,328
- 你是对的，你是对的  - 哇
- You're right. You're right.  - Wow.

84
00:07:17,403 --> 00:07:21,635
听我说，我们离开，好吗？就我们俩
Look, we'll... We'll go away, all right? Just us.

85
00:07:22,275 --> 00:07:23,435
太晚了，本
It's too late, Ben.

86
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:26,308
我不知道我还有什么没说过的能对你说
I don't know what I can say to you that I haven't said already.

87
00:07:26,379 --> 00:07:28,813
是时候挽救我自己了
95 It's time for me to rescue myself.

88
00:07:36,189 --> 00:07:38,953
可能是我该搬出去
Maybe... Maybe I should be the one to move out.

89
00:07:39,025 --> 00:07:40,117
嗨，这是海伦
Hi, you've reached Helen.

90
00:07:40,193 --> 00:07:41,319
和本的家
And Ben.

91
00:07:41,394 --> 00:07:42,418
请留言
Leave a message.

92
00:07:42,495 --> 00:07:44,622
你甚至不知道这房里的东西在哪
You don't even know where anything is in this house.

93
00:07:44,697 --> 00:07:45,857
还是这样简单的多
It's much easier this way.

94
00:07:45,932 --> 00:07:48,400
二级军士长，请向基地报道
Senior Chief, please report to base.

95
00:07:49,435 --> 00:07:52,529
我能…能改的，我…
I can... I can fix this, all right? I...

96
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,273
我能
I can...

97
00:07:56,976 --> 00:07:58,534
我能改的
I can fix this.

98
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:02,248
告诉我怎么做
Just tell me what to do.

99
00:08:02,949 --> 00:08:04,678
告诉我怎么做
Tell me what to do.

100
00:08:11,124 --> 00:08:12,785
- 让我走就好  - 不
- Just let me go.  - No.

101
00:08:13,593 --> 00:08:15,925
- 让我走  - 不
- Just let me go.  - No.

102
00:08:24,137 --> 00:08:26,071
你该接的
You should answer that.

103
00:08:28,374 --> 00:08:32,310
6096号救援直升机待命 救生员一号，回基地
Ready rescue helo 6096. Swimmer One, return to base.

104
00:08:33,479 --> 00:08:36,277
- 我不想失去她  - 那就改
- I don't wanna lose her.  - Then change.

105
00:08:36,349 --> 00:08:39,011
本，我们这样的讨论有多少回了
Ben, how many times have we had this conversation?

106
00:08:39,085 --> 00:08:43,112
你唯一的办法就是放弃，去做文职
The only way for you to save it is to give this up and fly a desk.

107
00:08:44,023 --> 00:08:46,821
没错，她只是想过日子
Exactly. She just wants to live.

108
00:08:48,494 --> 00:08:51,327
说不定我们能找个兴趣活动 我们都有兴趣的
Hey, maybe we can get a hobby. Both of us.

109
00:08:51,965 --> 00:08:53,865
比如钓鱼
Something like fishing.

110
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,494
- 钓鱼？  - 是啊
- Fishing?  - Yeah.

111
00:08:55,568 --> 00:08:57,934
我们这样的人不钓鱼，卡尔
Guys like us don't fish, Carl.

112
00:08:58,004 --> 00:09:00,165
这会有用的，一向有用
It'll work out. Always does.

113
00:09:01,674 --> 00:09:05,667
我问你个问题吧，说真的 我现在约她出去是不是太快了？
Let me ask you something, seriously. Is it too soon for me to ask her out?

114
00:09:05,878 --> 00:09:07,175
大概吧
I guess so.

115
00:09:10,250 --> 00:09:12,150
求救！求救！求救！
Mayday! Mayday! Mayday!

116
00:09:12,218 --> 00:09:14,209
这里是大海女王号货船
This is cargo vessel Seaqueen.

117
00:09:14,821 --> 00:09:17,984
我们在北纬55度12分
We're at 55 degrees, 12 minutes north.

118
00:09:18,057 --> 00:09:20,821
西经167度10分
167 degrees, 10 minutes west.

119
00:09:22,362 --> 00:09:23,488
船进水了
We're taking on water.

120
00:09:24,097 --> 00:09:27,362
我们要弃船，重复，弃船
We're abandoning ship. I repeat, abandoning ship.

121
00:09:34,607 --> 00:09:37,906
儿子，看着我，你会没事的，听到吗？
Son, look at me. Look at me. You're gonna be okay. Got that?

122
00:09:37,977 --> 00:09:40,104
听到吗？我们会没事的
Got that? We're gonna be okay.

123
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:42,270
没事的
Okay.

124
00:09:57,263 --> 00:09:59,356
尾翼除冰警告灯亮了
We have a tail rotor de-ice caution light.

125
00:09:59,432 --> 00:10:00,558
- 有什么相关警告吗？  - 没有
- Any secondaries?  - No.

126
00:10:00,633 --> 00:10:02,726
断路器还在，所以肯定是失效了
Circuit breakers are in, so it definitely has failed,

127
00:10:02,802 --> 00:10:04,235
但那没有什么冰啊
but we're not building up any ice.

128
00:10:04,304 --> 00:10:07,705
- 油量如何？  - 还能撑40分钟
- How's the fuel?  - Forty minutes to bingo.

129
00:10:07,774 --> 00:10:10,072
- 好，接管操纵杆  - 好，接管操纵了
- All right, take the stick.  - Okay, I have the controls.

130
00:10:10,143 --> 00:10:11,542
好啦，现在是暂停时间，各位
All right, huddle time, boys.

131
00:10:11,611 --> 00:10:13,977
除冰误警，油量很低
We have a de-ice fail. We're low on fuel.

132
00:10:14,047 --> 00:10:17,813
手册说我们应该避免我们的损失 你觉得呢，本？
The rulebook says we cut our losses. What do you think, Ben?

133
00:10:18,284 --> 00:10:20,844
我们要是回家，他们就会死，比尔
Well, we go home, they die, Bill.

134
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:28,321
科迪亚克行动中心，行动中心 这是海岸警卫队6096号
Ops Cent Kodiak, Ops Cent Kodiak, this is Coast Guard 6096.

135
00:10:28,394 --> 00:10:30,362
尾翼除冰警告灯亮了
We have a tail rotor de-ice caution light,

136
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:31,897
但我们要继续救援
but we are pressing on.

137
00:10:31,964 --> 00:10:34,524
6096号，有情况就向我们汇报
6096, keep us updated on your status.

138
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,397
- 6096号…  - 接通维修部主管
- 6096...  - Get the maintenance chief on the line.

139
00:10:36,469 --> 00:10:37,902
我想知道他对此有何意见
I wanna know what he thinks about this.

140
00:10:56,322 --> 00:10:58,813
计算机说风速在60到85节
Computer's saying the winds are 60 to 85 knots.

141
00:10:58,891 --> 00:11:00,153
我要把你的高度计关掉
I'm turning your bear alt off.

142
00:11:00,226 --> 00:11:02,717
- 你现在靠自己感觉高度了  - 收到
Roger.

143
00:11:02,795 --> 00:11:05,286
低点，低点，右面，水里有残骸
Lower! Lower! Right side. Debris in water.

144
00:11:05,365 --> 00:11:08,061
- 请求打开舱门  - 收到，开舱门
Roger. Open door.

145
00:11:09,902 --> 00:11:11,893
科迪亚克中心，6096号到现场了
Kodiak Ops, 6096 is on-scene.

146
00:11:11,971 --> 00:11:14,872
水里有大量残骸，进行表面搜寻
We have heavy debris in the water. Commencing cover search.

147
00:11:30,056 --> 00:11:31,546
标定并记录位置
Mark and note position.

148
00:11:33,326 --> 00:11:34,816
我要下去了
I'm going in.

149
00:11:37,897 --> 00:11:40,957
他们死了，本，他们死了
They're dead, Ben. Ben, they're dead!

150
00:11:41,033 --> 00:11:42,762
我们并不知道
We don't know that.

151
00:11:43,035 --> 00:11:45,868
有六名落水者，绑在一起 没有生命迹象
There's six PIWs all tied together. No signs of life.

152
00:11:47,006 --> 00:11:48,371
我觉得可能太迟了
I think we may be too late.

153
00:11:48,441 --> 00:11:51,501
不是我们的事，他们在现场 他们会做评估的
Not our call. They're on-scene. They'll make the assessment.

154
00:11:51,944 --> 00:11:53,673
请求下水，长官
Requesting to get wet, sir.

155
00:11:53,746 --> 00:11:56,180
我不是让你去拽尸体的 起码不是这样天气
I ain't sending you fishing for bodies, not in this.

156
00:11:56,249 --> 00:11:58,683
那，救父子呢？
Well, how about fathers and sons?

157
00:12:01,187 --> 00:12:04,748
照明弹，有个活着的，有个活着的
Flare! Flare! We got a live one here. We got a live one!

158
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:10,759
给你5分钟，然后我们就拉你上来
You got five minutes, then we're hauling your ass back up.

159
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:12,957
科迪亚克中心，这是海岸警卫队6096号
Kodiak Ops, this is Coast Guard 6096.

160
00:12:13,032 --> 00:12:15,466
水中有人，我们要派出救生员
We have people in the water, and we are deploying our swimmer.

161
00:12:15,535 --> 00:12:17,696
6096号，这是科迪亚克中心，收到
6096, Kodiak Ops, copy.

162
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:20,204
有个人拿着照明弹，我看不到其他动作
One's holding the flare. I see no other movement.

163
00:12:20,273 --> 00:12:21,297
收到
Roger that.

164
00:12:21,374 --> 00:12:22,671
准备派出救生员
Swimmer's ready to deploy.

165
00:12:22,742 --> 00:12:25,802
- 检查救生员  - 收到，检查救生员
- Check swimmer.  - Roger. Checking swimmer.

166
00:12:29,415 --> 00:12:32,111
救生员全副武装，检查完毕
Swimmer's dressed out. Checklist is complete.

167
00:12:32,185 --> 00:12:33,652
5分钟
Five minutes.

168
00:12:37,423 --> 00:12:39,050
救生员下水了
Swimmer's away.

169
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:47,857
救生员安全
Swimmer's okay.

170
00:12:47,934 --> 00:12:51,165
- 离开，向左后退30英尺  - 离开，向左后退
- Clear to move back and left 30.  - Clear back and left.

171
00:13:11,224 --> 00:13:12,623
油量如何？
How we looking on fuel there?

172
00:13:12,692 --> 00:13:14,922
还能撑2分钟
Two minutes to bingo.

173
00:13:21,701 --> 00:13:24,397
我是海岸警卫队救生员 来救你的，孩子
I'm a Coast Guard rescue swimmer here to help you, son.

