00:26:31,990 --> 00:26:34,891
起来跑到松树那再回来，出发
Pop tall to the lone pine and back! Go!

341
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:38,327
快跑，动起来，出发
Move your ass! Let's move it! Get it going!

342
00:26:38,497 --> 00:26:39,521
快跑
Let's go.

343
00:26:41,767 --> 00:26:42,756
快跑
Let's go.

344
00:26:43,001 --> 00:26:44,298
让他们回来
Bring them back.

345
00:26:44,369 --> 00:26:47,338
- 回来  - 快跑，回去
Circle back!  - HALL: Let's go! Get back here!

346
00:26:47,406 --> 00:26:48,737
- 回来站队  - 快点
Get back in line!  - INSTRUCTOR: Let's move!

347
00:26:48,807 --> 00:26:50,570
- 站好队  - 快跑，快，快
- Back in formation.  - Let's move, move, move!

348
00:26:50,642 --> 00:26:52,542
站好队
Back in formation.

349
00:26:53,612 --> 00:26:56,137
俯卧撑姿势，二级军士长来检查
Lean and rest. Senior Chief on deck.

350
00:27:30,482 --> 00:27:31,744
起来
Pop tall.

351
00:27:33,018 --> 00:27:34,042
乌拉
Oorah!

352
00:27:34,686 --> 00:27:36,517
我不在乎你是谁
I don't care who you are,

353
00:27:36,788 --> 00:27:38,722
从哪来，到哪去
where you are from or where you are going.

354
00:27:38,790 --> 00:27:40,724
我只在乎一件事
I care about one thing and one thing only.

355
00:27:40,792 --> 00:27:43,784
就是将来要求你们救的人
That is the future victims that you will be asked to save.

356
00:27:43,862 --> 00:27:47,628
如果我觉得你救不了他们 我就会开除你，懂了吗？
If I feel that you will fail them, I will fail you, understood?

357
00:27:47,699 --> 00:27:49,997
明白，二级军士长
Yes, Senior Chief!

358
00:27:52,104 --> 00:27:54,800
霍吉，你从哪来？
Hodge. Where are you from, Hodge?

359
00:27:54,873 --> 00:27:57,068
我来自新泽西州提奈克 二级军士长!
I'm from Teaneck, New Jersey, Senior Chief!

360
00:27:57,142 --> 00:27:59,235
霍吉这是第三次尝试了
Hodge is our triple repeat.

361
00:28:00,078 --> 00:28:02,546
你这回打算通过吗？三进宫？
Do you plan on making it this time, threepeat?

362
00:28:02,614 --> 00:28:03,876
我真的希望可以，二级军士长
I really hope to, Senior Chief.

363
00:28:03,949 --> 00:28:05,780
好，不过，希望不能让你浮起来，霍吉
Yeah, well, hope don't float, Hodge.

364
00:28:05,851 --> 00:28:08,877
你最好开始学习逆流而游而不是顺流而下
You better start to learn to swim against the current and not with it.

365
00:28:08,954 --> 00:28:10,854
遵命，二级军士长
Aye, aye, Senior Chief.

366
00:28:11,623 --> 00:28:12,885
费舍
Fisch.

367
00:28:14,259 --> 00:28:16,591
费舍，你为什么要来？
Fisch. Why are you here, Fisch?

368
00:28:17,162 --> 00:28:20,063
我要来超出你的预期 二级军士长
I'm here to exceed your expectations, Senior Chief.

369
00:28:20,132 --> 00:28:23,659
我从心底就是救生员 生来如此，水中长大，乌拉
I'm a rescue swimmer at heart, born, bred and water-fed. Oorah!

370
00:28:24,536 --> 00:28:27,198
哇，我猜你整个早上都在练这个吧
Wow. I bet you practiced that all morning.

371
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:30,433
费舍尔是高中游泳冠军
Mr. Fischer is our high school swim champ.

372
00:28:30,509 --> 00:28:33,307
他拿到了常春藤所有学校的奖学金
He's had scholarships to every lvy League.

373
00:28:33,745 --> 00:28:37,306
哦，对不起，我没意识到他这么合格
Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't realize that he was so qualified.

374
00:28:37,516 --> 00:28:39,984
我是说，你在池子里创造记录吗？
I mean, you set records in a pool?

375
00:28:40,819 --> 00:28:41,877
太棒了
That's amazing.

376
00:28:41,953 --> 00:28:45,684
我猜最深的地方大概有八尺深吧？
I'll bet it was like, what, eight feet deep in the deep end?

377
00:28:47,225 --> 00:28:49,420
要是你的鼻塞不起作用怎么办？
What if your nose plug didn't work?

378
00:28:49,494 --> 00:28:52,588
如果其他救生员占了你的泳道呢？
What if another swimmer had cut into your lane?

379
00:28:56,001 --> 00:28:59,129
看在上帝份上，你可能会死的
For the love of God, you could have been killed.

380
00:29:00,472 --> 00:29:03,407
你们日程上安排你们今早进行体力测试
Your schedule says that you will perform a PT test this morning.

381
00:29:03,475 --> 00:29:05,340
这没有必要
That will not be necessary.

382
00:29:05,410 --> 00:29:08,072
你们被召来在水中服役
Water is where you've been called to serve.

383
00:29:08,146 --> 00:29:10,011
那你们就在水里测试好了
Water is where you will be tested.

384
00:29:15,187 --> 00:29:17,917
这将替代你们的体力测试
This will serve in place of your PT in-test.

385
00:29:17,989 --> 00:29:20,549
考试结果只有通过或不通过
This is a golno-go exercise.

386
00:29:21,927 --> 00:29:24,395
你们要踩水一个小时
You will tread water for one hour.

387
00:29:24,696 --> 00:29:29,030
你碰了墙，不通过 碰了底，不通过
You touch the wall, you fail. You touch the bottom, you fail.

388
00:29:29,100 --> 00:29:31,125
不通过就回家
You fail and you go home.

389
00:29:32,037 --> 00:29:35,200
军士长，本校执行的是两次不通过制度
Senior, this school operates on a two-challenge rule.

390
00:29:35,273 --> 00:29:37,298
你不能第一天就开除人啊
You can't throw them out on their first day.

391
00:29:37,375 --> 00:29:39,400
如果你在暖水池都撑不过去
If you cannot survive in a warm pool of water,

392
00:29:39,478 --> 00:29:42,845
这就没你什么事了，全班明白了吗？
then you have no business being here. Does this class understand?

393
00:29:42,914 --> 00:29:44,211
明白，二级军士长
Yes, Senior Chief!

394
00:29:44,282 --> 00:29:46,273
乌拉，5506班
Oorah, Class 5506.

395
00:29:46,351 --> 00:29:49,047
谁能告诉我救生员的座右铭
Now, who here can tell me the rescue swimmer's motto?

396
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:50,951
“舍己为人”，二级军士长
"So others may live," Senior Chief!

397
00:29:51,022 --> 00:29:53,513
喔，我觉得安全点了
Oh, I feel safer already.

398
00:29:53,592 --> 00:29:56,686
你愿意牺牲自己让他人活下去吗？金鱼？
You willing to sacrifice your life so others may live, Goldfish?

399
00:29:56,761 --> 00:29:58,626
是的，二级军士长
Yes, I am, Senior Chief.

400
00:29:58,697 --> 00:30:03,225
那你得正确努力 我要你们所有人都好好想想这个
You will have to earn that right. I want all of you to think about that.

401
00:30:04,636 --> 00:30:06,797
总有这样的时候
There's going to come a time

402
00:30:07,472 --> 00:30:11,272
你们会筋疲力尽，想要放弃了
when you reach the point of exhaustion and you wanna give up.

403
00:30:11,743 --> 00:30:14,735
问题是，你们会不会
Question is, will you?

404
00:30:25,657 --> 00:30:28,649
有三个字母能让你解脱
There are three letters that will set you free.

405
00:30:28,727 --> 00:30:32,163
DOR，自愿退出
DOR. Drop on Request.

406
00:30:50,015 --> 00:30:51,004
看看那
Look at that.

407
00:30:52,751 --> 00:30:54,275
浪费时间
Waste of time.

408
00:31:02,093 --> 00:31:04,721
- 你还好吗？  - 嘿，加油，待在上面
- You all right?  - Hey. Come on, stay up.

409
00:31:13,972 --> 00:31:15,405
谁帮帮他
Somebody help him out.

410
00:31:17,175 --> 00:31:19,143
嘿，他沉下去了
Hey, he's going under, man!

411
00:31:20,245 --> 00:31:21,576
帮帮他
Help him out.

412
00:31:22,247 --> 00:31:23,714
快啊
Come on!

413
00:31:27,953 --> 00:31:29,944
- 帮帮他  - 帮帮他
- Help him out.  - Help him out!

414
00:31:41,232 --> 00:31:42,927
嘿，放松点，伙计
Guys, relax, man!

415
00:31:43,635 --> 00:31:44,932
加油啊
Come on.

416
00:31:47,005 --> 00:31:48,495
加油
Come on, man.

417
00:31:48,907 --> 00:31:50,534
你被开除了
You're dismissed.

418
00:31:51,309 --> 00:31:53,834
- 我肌肉痉挛了  - 你死了
- I cramped up.  - You're gone.

419
00:31:55,213 --> 00:31:56,840
走吧，里昂，出来，快点
Let's go, Lyons, out of the water. Hurry up.

420
00:31:56,915 --> 00:31:58,940
- 快点  - 快点
Let's go.

421
00:32:00,719 --> 00:32:02,209
站起来
On your feet.

422
00:32:03,154 --> 00:32:07,989
物理学第一课，各位： 有肌肉并不会浮起来
First lesson in physics, people: Muscle does not float.

423
00:32:10,028 --> 00:32:12,462
沃特森上士，让他们出池子
Petty Officer Watson, pull them out of the pool.

424
00:32:12,530 --> 00:32:13,690
遵命，二级军士长
Aye, aye, Senior Chief.

425
00:32:13,765 --> 00:32:14,993
快点，出池子
Let's go, people, out of the water.

426
00:32:16,234 --> 00:32:17,462
快点，动起来
Hurry up! Let's move, people!

427
00:32:17,535 --> 00:32:19,765
快点，快点
Hurry up! Hurry up!

428
00:32:19,838 --> 00:32:21,806
版主，来这
Class leader, right here.

429
00:32:26,678 --> 00:32:30,273
我以为你说你愿意牺牲自己救他人的
I thought you said you were willing to sacrifice your life for another.

430
00:32:31,182 --> 00:32:32,843
是的，二级军士长
I am, Senior Chief.

431
00:32:32,917 --> 00:32:36,679
那他向你求救时，干嘛不救自己的队友
Then why didn't you save your teammate when he reached out for you?

432
00:32:39,090 --> 00:32:42,548
我没意识到我们是整队合作的，二级军士长
I wasn't aware we were working as a team, Senior Chief.

433
00:32:43,128 --> 00:32:45,824
这是我们唯一的工作方式，游泳冠军
That's the only way we work, swim champ.

434
00:32:49,367 --> 00:32:51,301
明白，二级军士长
Aye, aye, Senior Chief.

435
00:33:03,415 --> 00:33:04,746
混蛋
Asshole.

436
00:33:04,816 --> 00:33:06,943
- 再说一遍  - 你听见我说的了
- Come again?  - You heard me.

437
00:33:07,018 --> 00:33:09,384
嘿，嘿，别动手
Hey, hey, hey! Ease up! Ease up!

438
00:33:10,321 --> 00:33:11,845
- 不值得  - 别
- It's not worth it.  - Come on.

439
00:33:11,923 --> 00:33:14,448
有个好消息，里昂 我的浮标维护船上有个空缺
Good news, Lyons. I think there's an opening on my buoy tender.

440
00:33:14,526 --> 00:33:16,824
我帮你推荐一下吧
I'll put in a word for you, huh?

441
00:33:19,364 --> 00:33:21,662
我会怀念那家伙的
I'm really gonna miss that guy.

442
00:33:27,405 --> 00:33:30,704
- 嘿，伙计，你干嘛？  - 你得回自己的铺位了
- Hey, man, what are you doing?  - Got your bunk back.

443
00:33:37,282 --> 00:33:39,443
- 上校  - 本，进来
Ben. Come in.

444
00:33:40,185 --> 00:33:41,584
你干的太快了
You work fast.

445
00:33:41,653 --> 00:33:44,383
里昂是我们最佳候选人之一
Lyons, he was one of our top candidates.

446
00:33:45,290 --> 00:33:47,690
有时你还得射杀人质呢
Sometimes you gotta shoot a hostage.

447
00:33:47,759 --> 00:33:51,160
嘿，我们都知道你是传奇人物
Look, we all know that you're a legend and all,

448
00:33:52,197 --> 00:33:54,791
但我们的课程已经被证实很有效果
but our program has been proven to work.

449
00:33:54,866 --> 00:33:57,994
训练和实际之间是有差距的，狂犬
There's a gap between training and what really happens out there, Cujo.

450
00:33:58,069 --> 00:33:59,468
- 哦，真的？  - 没错
- Oh, really?  - That's right.

451
00:33:59,537 --> 00:34:00,970
我的目的就是要缩小这个差距
My intention is to narrow that gap.

452
00:34:01,039 --> 00:34:04,031
如果有谁有不同意见
Now, if someone has a problem with that idea,

453
00:34:04,709 --> 00:34:06,734
我洗耳恭听
I'd like to hear about it.

454
00:34:11,216 --> 00:34:13,514
这就是我们要做的吗？长官
Is this how it's gonna be, sir?

455
00:34:16,354 --> 00:34:17,719
没错
Yes, it is.

456
00:34:19,057 --> 00:34:22,254
- 请求离开，长官  - 批准
Permission to be dismissed, sir?  - CAPTAIN: Granted.

457
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:31,792
快走，快走，靠紧
Let's go. Let's go. Keep it together. Look tight!

458
00:34:31,870 --> 00:34:33,735
靠紧，快走，动起来
Keep it together. Let's go. Let's move.

459
00:34:33,805 --> 00:34:37,434
你们有三分钟穿好装备，全部装备
You've got three minutes to get this gear on. All of it.

460
00:34:37,809 --> 00:34:39,106
预备，开始
Set! Go!

461
00:34:42,680 --> 00:34:43,669
快
Let's go.

462
00:34:48,119 --> 00:34:49,711
准备好了吗？
Are you ready?

463
00:34:55,026 --> 00:34:56,823
加油，救生员
Come on, rescue swimmer!

464
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:00,595
别放弃
Don't quit on me.

465
00:35:16,147 --> 00:35:17,978
听见了吗？
Do you hear me?

466
00:35:18,049 --> 00:35:19,448
听见了吗？
Do you hear me?

467
00:35:19,717 --> 00:35:23,278
起来，起来
Pop tall! Pop tall! Pop tall!

468
00:35:26,057 --> 00:35:30,790
如果你犯了个错，就认错 吸取教训继续
If you make a mistake, just fess up to it. Take your licks and we'll press on.

469
00:35:31,062 --> 00:35:34,554
每个人都会为笨嘴付出代价
Everybody now is gonna pay for your potty mouth.

470
00:35:34,632 --> 00:35:37,726
- 下，上  - 一
-Down. Up  - One!

471
00:35:37,802 --> 00:35:38,962
下
Down.

472
00:35:39,037 --> 00:35:40,299
- 上  - 三
- Up  - Three!

473
00:35:40,371 --> 00:35:41,770
下，上
Down. Up.

474
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,000
五，六
Five! Six!

475
00:35:43,090 --> 00:35:45,050
- 继续  - 七
- Forward.  - Seven!

476
00:35:49,180 --> 00:35:50,442
你疯了吗？
Are you crazy?

477
00:35:50,648 --> 00:35:52,343
我是指挥官，起来
I'm the commander! Get up!

478
00:35:52,417 --> 00:35:54,885
- 乌拉  - 趴下，趴下
Oorah!  - Get down! Get down!

479
00:35:55,787 --> 00:35:56,811
乌拉
Oorah!

480
00:36:04,395 --> 00:36:05,384
下去
Go.

481
00:36:19,744 --> 00:36:20,733
乌拉
Oorah.

482
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:23,469
乌拉
Oorah.

483
00:36:23,882 --> 00:36:24,871
乌拉
Oorah!

484
00:36:44,135 --> 00:36:46,603
氯气中毒会死吗？
Can you die from chlorine poisoning?

485
00:36:46,905 --> 00:36:49,430
我都感觉不到自己的腿了，我是说真的
I can't feel my legs. I'm serious.

486
00:36:50,475 --> 00:36:52,875
我不知道你们怎样，但是我感觉不错
I don't know about you guys, but I feel good.

487
00:36:52,944 --> 00:36:56,004
这个叫朗道的，完全不按规矩来
This Randall guy, he's operating on some whole other cylinder.

488
00:36:56,080 --> 00:36:59,072
这算啥，两个星期 他差不多都开除了一半人了
What is it, two weeks, and he's failed almost half the class already?

489
00:36:59,150 --> 00:37:00,549
他是传奇人物
He's a legend.

490
00:37:00,618 --> 00:37:02,449
他们说他救过两百多人
They say he's got something like 200 saves.

491
00:37:02,520 --> 00:37:04,283
我听说是三百
I heard it was 300.

492
00:37:04,355 --> 00:37:06,346
谁管他救过多少？
Who cares what his number is?

493
00:37:06,424 --> 00:37:08,892
他要是这么牛，来这干嘛
If he's such a stud, what's he doing here?

494
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:10,587
大家感觉如何啊
How we feeling, boys?

495
00:37:11,195 --> 00:37:12,594
嘿，Z，你要去哪？
Hey, Z, where you going?

496
00:37:12,664 --> 00:37:15,531
我姐姐最好的朋友要结婚了
My sister's best friend is getting married,

497
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:17,465
他们要在城里搞个大仪式
and they're having a big reception downtown.

498
00:37:17,535 --> 00:37:19,400
我答应她我会去的
I promised her I'd go.

499
00:37:20,071 --> 00:37:22,301
等等，你是说结婚典礼？
Wait, you said wedding reception?

500
00:37:41,125 --> 00:37:42,820
- 恭喜  - 谢谢
- Congratulations.  - Thanks.

501
00:37:42,894 --> 00:37:43,883
嗨
Hi.

502
00:37:44,162 --> 00:37:45,993
- 恭喜  - 嗨
- Congratulations.  - Hi.

503
00:37:46,064 --> 00:37:47,053
很高兴见到你
Nice to meet you.

504
00:37:47,465 --> 00:37:51,902
是的，阿拉斯加州科迪亚克 海伦・朗道的号码
Yes, Kodiak, Alaska. The number for Helen Randall.

505
00:37:55,707 --> 00:37:58,141
好，那试试海伦・佛里曼
Okay, try Helen Freeman.

506
00:38:01,012 --> 00:38:02,411
没错
You betcha.

507
00:38:08,553 --> 00:38:11,021
我是海伦，请留言
Hi, you've reached Helen. Leave a message.

508
00:38:11,923 --> 00:38:14,585
海伦，我是本，天，这太奇怪了
Helen, it's Ben. Jesus, that was weird.

509
00:38:15,159 --> 00:38:18,617
从我们长大就没用过你的娘家姓
Haven't had to use your maiden name since we were kids.

510
00:38:19,163 --> 00:38:22,621
海伦，如果你在，请接我电话 我们得谈谈
Helen, if you're there, just pick up. We need to talk.

511
00:38:26,337 --> 00:38:27,326
求你了
Please.

512
00:38:39,751 --> 00:38:41,548
好吧，好吧
All right. All right.

513
00:38:42,186 --> 00:38:45,587
敬失败者，敬通过第一阶段测试的
To those who have fallen, to those who have survived Phase 1.

514
00:38:45,656 --> 00:38:47,453
- 干杯  - 干杯
