01:13:14,762 --> 01:13:18,391
就像那边的小孩子一样 猜猜谁会出任务？
like these little guys over here, guess who goes out?

1020
01:13:18,465 --> 01:13:19,989
没错，是我们
That's right, we do.

1021
01:13:20,067 --> 01:13:22,763
听着，亲爱的，你得小声点，好吗？
Look, honey, you better keep it down in here, okay?

1022
01:13:22,836 --> 01:13:24,770
好的，亲爱的 她叫我“亲爱的”
Okay, honey. She called me "honey."

1023
01:13:26,340 --> 01:13:27,534
好的，亲爱的
Okay, honey.

1024
01:13:27,608 --> 01:13:30,600
当上帝从天而降
But when God himself reaches down from heaven...

1025
01:13:31,312 --> 01:13:34,179
- 他会怎么做，杰克，当他…  - 把房子从地上撕裂
- What does he do, Jake, when he...  - Rips houses off the foundation.

1026
01:13:34,248 --> 01:13:37,615
当上帝把房子从地上撕裂，我们出任务
When God himself rips houses off the foundation, we go out,

1027
01:13:37,685 --> 01:13:39,380
因为我们是救生员
because we are rescue swimmers,

1028
01:13:39,453 --> 01:13:42,047
这是我们的工作，我们干的就是这个
and that is our job, and that's what we do.

1029
01:13:42,122 --> 01:13:44,249
你应该重新检查一下罗盘
You might wanna recheck your compass.

1030
01:13:44,325 --> 01:13:46,725
这里可不是什么烂海盗来的酒吧
This ain't no puddle pirate bar.

1031
01:13:55,402 --> 01:13:58,235
没问题，我们马上就走
No problem, because we were just leaving anyway.

1032
01:13:58,305 --> 01:13:59,966
- 坐下，霍吉  - 杰克
- Sit down, Hodge.  - Jake.

1033
01:14:00,040 --> 01:14:01,735
- 把酒喝完  - 杰克
- Finish your beer.  - Jake.

1034
01:14:01,809 --> 01:14:03,436
对，坐下，霍吉
Yeah, sit, Hodge.

1035
01:14:04,111 --> 01:14:05,874
伙计，这是我的啤酒
That's my beer, man.

1036
01:14:10,884 --> 01:14:12,351
喝完了吗？
Finished now?

1037
01:14:14,088 --> 01:14:15,953
祝你愉快
Must be happy hour.

1038
01:14:20,961 --> 01:14:21,950
嘿！
Hey!

1039
01:14:23,464 --> 01:14:24,488
后退
Back off.

1040
01:14:27,067 --> 01:14:29,558
来这里的都是退休海军
Everyone in this place is retired Navy.

1041
01:14:29,636 --> 01:14:32,366
嘿，嘿 我什么时候才能用电话？
Hey. Hey, when do I get that phone call?

1042
01:14:33,006 --> 01:14:36,464
我知道我有权力打电话 什么时候给我电话打？
I know I get a phone call. When do I get my phone call?

1043
01:14:41,749 --> 01:14:43,273
女士，非常抱歉
Ma'am, I am sorry,

1044
01:14:43,350 --> 01:14:45,978
如果20分钟没人来，我可要把桌子给别人了
but if nobody come in 20 minutes, I need the table.

1045
01:14:46,353 --> 01:14:47,411
- 好的  - 对不起
- Okay.  - I'm sorry.

1046
01:14:47,488 --> 01:14:48,580
好吧
Yeah.

1047
01:14:52,960 --> 01:14:54,894
她再也不会和我说话了
She's never gonna talk to me again.

1048
01:14:55,829 --> 01:14:58,229
你知道他们会把我们踢出去的，对吗？
You know they're gonna kick us out for this, right?

1049
01:14:58,298 --> 01:14:59,458
是的
Yep.

1050
01:15:03,670 --> 01:15:05,900
至少他们不会说我们是自己退出的
Least they can't say we quit.

1051
01:15:06,974 --> 01:15:11,240
我办不到的 长官说的对，每次我都紧张
I was never gonna make it, anyway. Skinner's right. Panic every time.

1052
01:15:12,613 --> 01:15:14,444
伙计，别管长官怎么说
Man, screw Skinner.

1053
01:15:15,883 --> 01:15:17,714
我是长官，来挣脱我
I'm Skinner. Break my hold.

1054
01:15:17,785 --> 01:15:20,276
嘿，伙计，你在做什么？ 来吧，费舍尔，放开我
Hey, what are you doing, man? Come on, Fischer, get off me.

1055
01:15:20,354 --> 01:15:21,616
时间有限，快点挣脱我
Clock's ticking. Break it.

1056
01:15:21,688 --> 01:15:24,919
费舍尔，你弄伤我了 费舍尔，放开我，伙计!
Fischer, you're hurting me, man. Fischer, get off me, man!

1057
01:15:25,926 --> 01:15:28,588
快点，费舍尔，你弄伤我了 费舍尔，放开！
Come on, Fischer, you're hurting me. Fischer, man, get off!

1058
01:15:28,662 --> 01:15:30,687
- 快他妈的挣脱我  - 费舍尔，放开我!
- Break the goddamn hold.  - Fischer, get off me, man!

1059
01:15:30,764 --> 01:15:33,358
- 快挣脱，霍吉  - 费舍尔，放开我!
- Break the goddamn hold, Hodge.  - Fischer, get off me!

1060
01:15:34,868 --> 01:15:36,529
我说，放开我!
I said, get off me!

1061
01:15:37,004 --> 01:15:38,198
好吧
All right.

1062
01:15:38,472 --> 01:15:41,669
你在水里的时候就该这样
Now, it's just like that when you're in the water.

1063
01:15:44,645 --> 01:15:47,705
好了，现在我们可以走了
Well, now. We could come back.

1064
01:15:48,182 --> 01:15:51,549
给你们点时间抽抽烟，说说枕边话什么的
Give you boys time for a smoke and some pillow talk.

1065
01:15:59,593 --> 01:16:00,855
你不能把我们踢出去
You can't kick us out.

1066
01:16:00,928 --> 01:16:03,055
这叫不守纪律，我们可以把你们踢了
It's called disorderly conduct, and yes, we can.

1067
01:16:03,130 --> 01:16:05,758
- 我们没有不及格  - 我们的专业包括遵守纪律
- We didn't fail at nothing.  - Our profession is all about control.

1068
01:16:05,833 --> 01:16:07,562
你们这方面都不及格
You both failed miserably in that department.

1069
01:16:07,634 --> 01:16:09,431
站在这里
Hold it right there.

1070
01:16:09,503 --> 01:16:11,300
- 军士长？  - 进来吧
- Senior?  - Yeah, come in.

1071
01:16:14,074 --> 01:16:16,201
他们的开除报告
Their disenrollment records.

1072
01:16:18,011 --> 01:16:19,342
酒吧斗殴？
Bar fight?

1073
01:16:20,848 --> 01:16:22,975
- 好了，带他们进来  - 军士长
- All right, bring them in.  - Senior.

1074
01:16:23,083 --> 01:16:24,414
进来吧
Square it.

1075
01:16:31,225 --> 01:16:34,422
这都是我的错，二级军事长 霍吉和这无关
It's all my fault, Senior Chief. Hodge had nothing to do with it.

1076
01:16:36,196 --> 01:16:38,391
- 是这样吗，霍吉？  - 没错
- That true, Hodge?  - It's true.

1077
01:16:42,302 --> 01:16:44,998
好吧，你解散吧
All right. Fine, you're dismissed.

1078
01:16:45,472 --> 01:16:49,431
- 二级军士长，我  - 我说了你已经解散了
- Senior Chief, I was...  - I said that you are dismissed.

1079
01:16:50,310 --> 01:16:51,572
走吧
Let's go.

1080
01:16:58,685 --> 01:17:01,415
因为我捍卫了海岸警卫队的尊严 你就要踢我走人吗？
You're gonna kick me out for defending the Coast Guard?

1081
01:17:01,889 --> 01:17:03,982
海岸警卫队有200年历史
The Coast Guard's been around for 200 years.

1082
01:17:04,057 --> 01:17:07,390
我想只有你这样的傻冒 会这样维护它的尊严
I doubt a couple of knuckleheads like yourself are gonna defend it.

1083
01:17:07,761 --> 01:17:08,989
坐下
Sit down.

1084
01:17:12,499 --> 01:17:16,094
我想和你平静下来平等地谈谈，但是
I've been trying to peel the layers back on you for a while now, and I...

1085
01:17:16,403 --> 01:17:17,631
我有一点不明白
I just don't get it.

1086
01:17:19,139 --> 01:17:21,232
我是说，这工作对于你这样的人来说
I mean, this kind of work seems a little remedial

1087
01:17:21,308 --> 01:17:22,332
似乎只是一种疗伤
for someone like yourself.

1088
01:17:22,409 --> 01:17:24,809
你知道，游泳冠军 常春藤每一个学校的奖学金
You know, big swim champ, offer to every lvy League.

1089
01:17:24,878 --> 01:17:27,540
你放弃一切到这和我们在一起
You give it all up to be here with us.

1090
01:17:28,815 --> 01:17:32,307
- 为什么？  - 我是为了拯救生命，二级军士长
- Why?  - I'm here to save lives, Senior Chief.

1091
01:17:36,623 --> 01:17:38,853
我和你的教练谈过了，杰克
I spoke with your coach, Jake.

1092
01:17:41,061 --> 01:17:43,529
- 好我的教练谈？  - 是的，我和你的教练谈了
- You spoke with my coach?  - Yeah, I spoke with your coach.

1093
01:17:43,597 --> 01:17:46,964
你的档案里有些东西让我很牵挂
Something in your file just kept hanging me up.

1094
01:17:47,034 --> 01:17:50,492
你第一年和第二年连续获得州里的冠军
You win the state championship your freshman and sophomore year

1095
01:17:50,571 --> 01:17:53,233
但后两年你没再去游
and then you don't swim the next two.

1096
01:17:53,507 --> 01:17:56,943
我只是个公立学校毕业的家伙
I'm just a public school guy, so pardon me,

1097
01:17:57,010 --> 01:18:00,776
我一直没有意识到，直到看到这些
but it didn't add up until now.

1098
01:18:06,987 --> 01:18:10,184
“科科・霍里华，100米混合泳冠军”
"Kirk Holloway, 100-meter medley winner,

1099
01:18:11,024 --> 01:18:13,492
“从车窗里甩了出去”
"thrown through the passenger window.

1100
01:18:13,560 --> 01:18:15,858
“当场死亡”
"Pronounced dead at the scene.

1101
01:18:17,364 --> 01:18:22,324
“艾比・科曼，美国1队，肺穿孔”
"Abe lkeman, first team All-American, lungs crushed.

1102
01:18:25,372 --> 01:18:29,331
“卡尔・山多夫，50米自由泳冠军”
"Carl Sandoval, 50-meter freestyle champ,

1103
01:18:29,409 --> 01:18:34,039
“送往医院的途中死于内出血”
"made it all the way to the hospital. Died of internal bleeding."

1104
01:18:43,590 --> 01:18:46,320
我想你都知道了
I guess you just know everything, then.

1105
01:18:47,160 --> 01:18:49,754
我知道失去队友是什么样的
I know what it's like to lose a team.

1106
01:18:51,198 --> 01:18:52,324
是吗
Yeah?

1107
01:18:52,599 --> 01:18:53,998
生活在一个小镇上
What about living in a small town

1108
01:18:54,067 --> 01:18:56,194
别人认为他杀了自己的兄弟
where everyone thinks that you killed their brother

1109
01:18:56,269 --> 01:18:57,827
儿子或是最好的朋友，会是什么感觉？
or their son or their best friend?

1110
01:18:57,904 --> 01:18:59,303
你知道那是什么感觉吗？
You know about that?

1111
01:19:00,240 --> 01:19:03,676
看来小镇上的人相互之间打招呼
Kind of small town where everyone still waves to everyone,

1112
01:19:04,911 --> 01:19:06,503
但不和你打招呼？
just not to you?

1113
01:19:08,915 --> 01:19:12,817
我读了报告，杰克 当时你的酒精含量为零
I read the report, Jake. Your blood alcohol was zip that night.

1114
01:19:13,854 --> 01:19:16,982
我猜是另一个冒失的司机开的车
I'm guessing there was a flip for designated driver.

1115
01:19:17,057 --> 01:19:18,354
你却被错怪
You lost.

1116
01:19:19,393 --> 01:19:21,486
猜猜就能解决问题？
Guess that just makes it all go away, huh?

1117
01:19:21,561 --> 01:19:24,792
不，没有解决任何问题 这只是一场意外
No, it doesn't make it all right. It just makes it an accident.

1118
01:19:25,298 --> 01:19:27,323
至少报告上这样说
At least that's how it reads.

1119
01:19:28,669 --> 01:19:30,330
那时你才16岁，杰克
You were 16 years old, Jake.

1120
01:19:30,404 --> 01:19:32,929
我不是你的牧师，但如果我是，我想
I'm not your priest, but if I was, I think...

1121
01:19:33,407 --> 01:19:35,500
我想我不会为难你
I think maybe you'd deserve a pass.

1122
01:19:39,046 --> 01:19:41,071
不为难我？
You're giving me a pass?

1123
01:19:41,248 --> 01:19:45,378
你以为你知道所有事 其实你什么都不是
You just think you know everything with your psychobabble bullshit.

1124
01:19:45,452 --> 01:19:47,477
为什么我在这里？为什么你在这里？
Why am I here? Why are you here?

1125
01:19:48,889 --> 01:19:51,585
你太老了只能干这个，你已经快不行了
You're too old to be doing this. You're washed-up here.

1126
01:19:51,658 --> 01:19:55,219
你可不想在池子里教小孩，我说的对吗？
You don't wanna be teaching a bunch of kids in a pool. Am I right?

1127
01:19:55,295 --> 01:19:58,696
我不在乎你看了什么说了什么
I don't give a shit what you read or who you talked to.

1128
01:19:58,765 --> 01:20:02,701
你根本不了解我，你不… 我能管好我自己
You don't know about me! You don't... I have me under control.

1129
01:20:07,240 --> 01:20:08,764
我能看出来
I can see that.

1130
01:20:27,894 --> 01:20:30,658
我和你唯一的区别是
The only difference between you and me is,

1131
01:20:32,199 --> 01:20:35,362
我没有帮在我手上 死去的人穿上衣服，杰克
I don't wear the ones I lost on my arm, Jake.

1132
01:20:43,810 --> 01:20:46,040
我知道你的处境，杰克
I know where you're at, Jake.

1133
01:20:46,947 --> 01:20:48,642
我也在那儿
I'm there myself.

1134
01:20:50,884 --> 01:20:54,411
每天我都会问自己 为什么我是幸存下来的那个人
I ask myself every day why I was the one that survived.

1135
01:20:59,726 --> 01:21:01,956
- 然后？  - 然后
- And?  - And...

1136
01:21:04,765 --> 01:21:06,289
如果我回答不了自己
And if I can't answer that for me,

1137
01:21:06,366 --> 01:21:09,767
我没办法试着向你解释
I'm certainly not going to try and answer it for you.

1138
01:21:14,574 --> 01:21:15,973
坐下
Have a seat.

1139
01:21:22,415 --> 01:21:25,543
我想让你成为其中一员
I want you to start being a member of this team,

1140
01:21:26,753 --> 01:21:28,618
你知道我指的是什么
the team you have now.

1141
01:21:29,890 --> 01:21:31,790
你很有天赋，杰克
You have a gift, Jake.

1142
01:21:32,159 --> 01:21:34,218
你是到这里来的最棒的队员
You're the best swimmer to come through this program,

1143
01:21:34,294 --> 01:21:35,488
不用很久，你能轻松通过的
hands down, by far.

1144
01:21:35,562 --> 01:21:37,496
你有整个纪录板去证明
You got a whole record board to prove it.

1145
01:21:37,564 --> 01:21:40,260
你知道我看到了什么吗？
But you know what I see when I look at it?

1146
01:21:40,333 --> 01:21:43,791
我看到有人足够快能够 第一个游到幸存者身边
I see someone fast enough who's gonna get there first.

1147
01:21:45,005 --> 01:21:47,132
我看到有人足够强壮能够支撑到最后
I see someone strong enough who's gonna last.

1148
01:21:47,207 --> 01:21:51,906
我看到有人能拯救别人救不了的人
I see someone who can save a life that maybe nobody else could.

1149
01:21:54,247 --> 01:21:57,375
你想以你的双手创造荣耀吗？
You really wanna honor the initials on your arm?

1150
01:21:58,685 --> 01:22:00,516
那就好好利用你的天赋吧
Then honor your gift.

1151
01:22:03,490 --> 01:22:05,617
救每一个你能救到的人，杰克
Save the ones you can, Jake.

1152
01:22:07,060 --> 01:22:10,427
其余的，我们得学会放手
The rest, we've gotta let go.

1153
01:22:21,241 --> 01:22:23,368
你是说你不会开除我？
Does this mean you're not gonna fail me?

1154
01:22:24,177 --> 01:22:27,943
为什么，就为了在酒吧帮助伙伴？
For what, backing up a buddy in a bar?

1155
01:22:30,851 --> 01:22:33,376
伙计，比起你我可有过更大的麻烦
Man, I got bigger problems than you.

1156
01:22:36,623 --> 01:22:40,150
我不知道你，要是我 我他妈的可要操起酒瓶子揍他了
I don't know about you, but I could use a fucking drink.

1157
01:22:44,998 --> 01:22:46,124
喔
Oops.

1158
01:22:48,635 --> 01:22:52,503
我今天晚上都在考虑纪录和责任之外的事
I'm gonna consider everything tonight off-record and off-duty.

1159
01:22:56,309 --> 01:22:57,469
这个是个邀请
That was an invite.

1160
01:22:58,278 --> 01:22:59,267
哦
Oh.

1161
01:23:03,617 --> 01:23:05,585
你一定是开玩笑
You gotta be kidding me.

1162
01:23:06,186 --> 01:23:09,883
- 他们是怎么称呼你的？  - “烂海盗”，这不是…
- What was it they called you?  - "Puddle pirates," but it's not...

1163
01:23:09,956 --> 01:23:13,687
别去了，军士长
I'm way over it, Senior Chief. This is...

1164
01:23:14,160 --> 01:23:17,527
- 好吧，看上去可不友善啊  - 我们就喝一杯酒
- Well, it's like sticks and stones.  - Well, we'll just have one beer.

1165
01:23:23,904 --> 01:23:27,772
很好，他们喝的烂醉
Great. They're angrier and drunker. Perfect.

1166
01:23:27,841 --> 01:23:30,241
嗨，2杯啤酒
Hi. Two beers.

1167
01:23:31,244 --> 01:23:33,872
- 你在开玩笑吧  - 我就是这么说的
- You gotta be kidding me.  - That's what I said.

1168
01:23:34,781 --> 01:23:37,409
听着，别给我惹事，明白吗？
Look, I don't want any trouble, okay?

1169
01:23:40,387 --> 01:23:42,821
他们都不喜欢我们，对吗？
They really don't like us, do they?

1170
01:23:42,889 --> 01:23:47,326
不 他们觉得比我们优秀 因为他们是打仗的
No. They think they're better than us because they're combat-oriented.

1171
01:23:48,495 --> 01:23:50,622
我们是海岸警卫队，杰克
We're the Coast Guard, Jake.

1172
01:23:50,730 --> 01:23:53,893
没有人会赏识我们，除非他们需要我们
Nobody really appreciates us until they need us.

1173
01:23:56,436 --> 01:23:57,698
是他吗？
That him?

1174
01:24:05,645 --> 01:24:06,703
是的
Yep.

1175
01:24:12,118 --> 01:24:15,451
在我们开始流血之前我先问你个问题
So let me ask you a question before we start bleeding.

1176
01:24:17,123 --> 01:24:21,150
你救的那么多人…具体数字是多少？
All those saves... What's your real number?

1177
01:24:28,101 --> 01:24:31,468
你是想死呢还是傻的可以？
Do you have a death wish, or are you just shit-stupid?

1178
01:24:32,806 --> 01:24:35,297
算是犯傻劲吧
I'm gonna go with stupid this time.

1179
01:24:35,375 --> 01:24:37,240
- 嗨  - 嗨
