1192
01:25:45,845 --> 01:25:49,246
你有什么要对我说的吗？
Is there anything you'd like to say to me?

1193
01:25:49,616 --> 01:25:50,640
比方说？
Like what?

1194
01:25:51,751 --> 01:25:53,719
我不知道，但我对你道歉了
I don't know, but I apologized to you.

1195
01:25:53,787 --> 01:25:55,550
我只是觉得，你知道
I just thought that, you know,

1196
01:25:55,622 --> 01:25:57,852
你以前可能说过些什么
there might be something you've said or done

1197
01:25:57,924 --> 01:25:59,892
那些你可以向我道歉的
that you'd like to apologize to me for.

1198
01:25:59,959 --> 01:26:01,017
为什么？
Why?

1199
01:26:02,729 --> 01:26:04,924
因为就该是这样的，我…
'Cause that's how it's done. I...

1200
01:26:05,298 --> 01:26:07,596
你知道吗，你真是太不会道歉了
You suck at apologies, you know that?

1201
01:26:07,700 --> 01:26:09,691
我是说你都没弄明白什么是道歉
I mean, you're missing the whole concept.

1202
01:26:20,547 --> 01:26:23,744
- 喂你好？  - 嗨，是我
Hello?  - JAKE: Hi. It's me.

1203
01:26:26,252 --> 01:26:29,813
你还好吗？发生什么了？我等了你2个小时
Are you okay? What happened? I mean, I waited for two hours.

1204
01:26:30,123 --> 01:26:34,253
嗯 听着，这很复杂
Yeah. No. Look, I'm really sorry. I...

1205
01:26:34,828 --> 01:26:36,022
怎么了？
What happened?

1206
01:26:36,129 --> 01:26:38,893
真的要说很久了
It's a really long story.

1207
01:26:40,433 --> 01:26:43,994
让我…这样说吧
Let me just... Let me put it this way.

1208
01:26:45,171 --> 01:26:49,835
这是我这辈子最好也是最坏的一天
It was the best worst night of my life.

1209
01:26:51,077 --> 01:26:52,874
好吧，我很高兴有人找到乐子了
Well, I'm glad someone had fun.

1210
01:26:58,218 --> 01:27:01,085
明天能见你吗？
Can I see you tomorrow night?

1211
01:27:01,488 --> 01:27:03,752
明天有家长会
I have parent-teacher conferences tomorrow.

1212
01:27:04,757 --> 01:27:06,384
那后天呢？
What about the next night?

1213
01:27:06,993 --> 01:27:09,154
我一周都有家长会
I have parent-teacher conferences all week.

1214
01:27:10,563 --> 01:27:13,555
- 你要甩了我吗？  - 不，杰克
You blowing me off?  - EMILY: No, Jake.

1215
01:27:14,767 --> 01:27:16,462
我不会这样做的
I wouldn't do that to somebody.

1216
01:27:18,571 --> 01:27:21,506
再过几个小时我得出发了 我要睡了
I gotta get up in a couple hours. I gotta go.

1217
01:27:21,674 --> 01:27:24,643
- 好的  - 再见
- Yep.  - Goodbye.

1218
01:27:35,188 --> 01:27:37,452
好了，你们还都记得该怎么做吧
All right, you know what we briefed on the ground.

1219
01:27:37,524 --> 01:27:40,152
和以前一样，我们要一起行动
Same thing. We're gonna stay together.

1220
01:27:40,226 --> 01:27:44,094
无论发生了什么事，你们要一起行动
No matter what happens out there, you stay together.

1221
01:27:44,531 --> 01:27:49,195
无论要做什么决定，一起行动
Whatever decision you make, you make as a team.

1222
01:27:52,272 --> 01:27:55,435
我们训练时从15到20英尺跳下去
We trained to freefall at 15 to 20 feet.

1223
01:27:56,075 --> 01:27:59,408
从50尺跳下去，就像跳进混凝土
You fall from 50 feet, it's like hitting concrete.

1224
01:27:59,812 --> 01:28:03,612
从80到100尺跳下去，你就没命了
You fall 80 to 100 feet, you die.

1225
