Swimmer's coming to the door.

1347
01:38:58,270 --> 01:38:59,794
记住，好吗？
Remember, all right?

1348
01:38:59,872 --> 01:39:04,241
海浪会把你冲到洞口
You got the whole weight of the ocean punching through that opening.

1349
01:39:04,310 --> 01:39:07,711
你得计算浪头
You gotta read the hydraulics, gotta count the waves,

1350
01:39:08,113 --> 01:39:10,081
然后等着回流
then wait for the flush.

1351
01:39:11,517 --> 01:39:13,144
检查救生员
Checking swimmer.

1352
01:39:13,886 --> 01:39:17,378
但愿你上课的时候仔细听了
Sure as hell hope you paid attention in class, Speedboat.

1353
01:39:39,445 --> 01:39:41,310
救生员入水
Swimmers in the water.

1354
01:39:41,547 --> 01:39:43,071
救生员良好
Swimmers okay.

1355
01:39:47,786 --> 01:39:50,880
救生员1号和2号进行交流
Swimmer Two is making contact with Swimmer One.

1356
01:40:26,825 --> 01:40:27,849
嘿
Hey!

1357
01:40:28,160 --> 01:40:29,184
这里!
Over here!

1358
01:40:29,261 --> 01:40:31,058
- 这里  - 这里!
- Here.  - Over here!

1359
01:40:31,130 --> 01:40:32,654
找到了，3点钟方向
Got them. Three o'clock.

1360
01:40:33,165 --> 01:40:34,530
这边
Right here.

1361
01:40:38,437 --> 01:40:40,769
我们是海岸警卫队救生员 我们来救援你们
We're rescue swimmers. We're gonna get you out of here.

1362
01:40:40,839 --> 01:40:42,864
真不敢相信你们真的来了
Can't believe you guys actually got here.

1363
01:40:42,942 --> 01:40:44,500
把手给我
Give me your hand.

1364
01:40:46,512 --> 01:40:47,706
只有你们两个？
Just the two of you?

1365
