1545
01:57:10,895 --> 01:57:12,192
扶好
Hold on.

1546
01:57:14,499 --> 01:57:16,899
1号救生员，1号救生员，快进来
Swimmer One, Swimmer One, come in.

1547
01:57:18,236 --> 01:57:20,329
救生员6034
Rescue swimmer, 6034.

1548
01:57:20,405 --> 01:57:22,305
费舍尔 进来，费舍尔
Fischer. Come in, Fischer.

1549
01:57:22,373 --> 01:57:24,603
1号救生员，1号救生员 进来
Swimmer One, Swimmer One, come in.

1550
01:57:24,676 --> 01:57:27,543
- 这是1号救生员  - 收到，1号救生员，继续
This is Swimmer One.  - Roger that, Swimmer One. Go ahead.

1551
01:57:27,612 --> 01:57:30,672
救生员1号，船里还有1个人，我去救他出来
Swimmer One. I got one down below. I'm gonna go down there.

1552
01:57:30,748 --> 01:57:34,240
救生员1号，我们只剩7分钟了
Swimmer One, be advised we've got seven minutes to bingo.

1553
01:57:34,352 --> 01:57:35,876
我下去了
I'm going down.

1554
01:57:47,865 --> 01:57:49,594
- 船长？  - 是我
Captain?  - CAPTAIN: Yeah!

1555
01:57:49,767 --> 01:57:50,859
船长？
Captain?

1556
01:57:54,872 --> 01:57:58,672
