Captain! I'm a rescue swimmer. I'm here to help you out.

1557
01:57:58,743 --> 01:58:02,270
你的腿卡住了还是断了？
Your leg is jammed in here? Or is it just closed...

1558
01:58:02,347 --> 01:58:04,076
我的整条腿
It's the whole leg!

1559
01:58:04,349 --> 01:58:07,284
我想要放开离合器，但是被卡住了
I tried to free the clutch and got stuck.

1560
01:58:08,920 --> 01:58:10,410
这是1号救生员
This is Swimmer One.

1561
01:58:10,488 --> 01:58:12,979
我在引擎室找到船长了，他的腿卡住了
I got the captain down here in the engine room. He's stuck.

1562
01:58:13,057 --> 01:58:14,388
我们需要一点时间
We're gonna be a little bit.

1563
01:58:14,459 --> 01:58:15,892
1号救生员，我们没有时间了
Swimmer One, we're about out of time.

1564
01:58:15,960 --> 01:58:18,554
船就要下沉了，我们还有2分钟
That boat's listing bad, and we're two minutes to bingo.

1565
01:58:18,629 --> 01:58:21,029
我不会丢下他的
I ain't leaving here without him.

1566
01:58:22,300 --> 01:58:24,996
派别人来援救我们，我要看着他
Send somebody back for us, 'cause I'm staying down here with him.

1567
01:58:25,069 --> 01:58:28,095
不行，1号救生员 我们要你尽快上来
Negative, Swimmer One. We need you topside ASAP.

1568
01:58:29,307 --> 01:58:31,673
1号救生员，6034
Swimmer One, 6034.

1569
01:58:32,343 --> 01:58:34,743
1号救生员，6034
Swimmer One, 6034.

1570
01:58:35,346 --> 01:58:38,577
科迪亚克，这是6034
Kodiak Ops, Kodiak Ops, this is 6034.

1571
01:58:38,649 --> 01:58:40,981
我们现在返回
Be advised we are RTB at this time.

1572
01:58:41,052 --> 01:58:43,077
我们把救生员留在现场
We are leaving the rescue swimmer on-scene.

1573
01:58:43,154 --> 01:58:45,315
重复一遍，我们把救生员留在现场
I say again, we are leaving our rescue swimmer on-scene.

1574
01:58:45,390 --> 01:58:46,823
我们还有直升机吗？
Who do we have left in the shop?

1575
01:58:46,891 --> 01:58:48,984
08号可以，但是没有救生员
08's all we've got left, sir, but no crew.

1576
01:58:49,060 --> 01:58:50,550
- 好的，快去启动  - 是，长官
- All right, get her online.  - Yes, sir.

1577
01:58:50,628 --> 01:58:53,722
上尉，我们准备出发
Lieutenant Krauss, suit up. We're handling this.

1578
01:58:54,866 --> 01:58:56,493
我要一个救生员
I need a swimmer.

1579
01:58:58,836 --> 01:59:00,201
别担心
Don't worry.

1580
01:59:00,304 --> 01:59:02,033
不，不会的，他们会把他救起来的
No, no, they'll get him.

1581
01:59:02,106 --> 01:59:03,232
别担心！别担心
Don't worry! Don't worry.

1582
01:59:16,721 --> 01:59:18,120
我们走
Here we go.

1583
01:59:34,138 --> 01:59:35,799
挺住，挺住
Hold on. Hold on.

1584
01:59:42,046 --> 01:59:44,173
- 准备好回家了吗  - 是的，伙计
- Ready to go home?  - Yeah, man.

1585
02:00:00,098 --> 02:00:01,725
船长 船长!
Captain. Captain!

1586
02:00:16,647 --> 02:00:19,411
- 可以出发了吗，上尉？  - 是的，长官
Are we cleared in, Lieutenant?  - KRAUSS: Aye, aye, Captain.

1587
02:00:19,484 --> 02:00:20,883
很好
Outstanding.

1588
02:00:37,668 --> 02:00:40,466
1号救生员，我是6008
Rescue Swimmer One, this is 6008.

1589
02:00:40,538 --> 02:00:41,630
能听见吗？
Do you read?

1590
02:00:41,706 --> 02:00:45,540
1号救生员，我是6008 能听见吗？
Come in, Rescue Swimmer One. 6008. Do you read?

1591
02:00:46,277 --> 02:00:48,245
回话，杰克
Come on, Jake, be there.

1592
02:01:05,463 --> 02:01:08,899
舱门已打开
Cabin door's coming open. Cabin door's open and locked.

1593
02:01:09,667 --> 02:01:12,932
好的，就在那里，甲板上没有人
All right, right there. Right side. Nobody onboard.

1594
02:01:13,905 --> 02:01:15,770
好的，我能看到
All right. I see what I want.

1595
02:01:15,840 --> 02:01:18,604
把我放下去，放到右边的角上
Just get me down. The right-hand corner.

1596
02:01:18,676 --> 02:01:20,268
当心别碰到绳索
Try to avoid the rigging.

1597
02:01:20,344 --> 02:01:22,403
救生员要求放到右边的角上
Okay, swimmer requests aft right-hand corner.

1598
02:01:22,480 --> 02:01:23,879
右边的角上
Aft right-hand corner.

1599
02:01:23,948 --> 02:01:25,279
好的，就这么办
Okay, this is what we're gonna do.

1600
02:01:25,349 --> 02:01:26,941
救生员准备，第二部分
Start a rescue checklist, part two,

1601
02:01:27,018 --> 02:01:28,952
救生员装备检查
for a harness deployment of the rescue swimmer.

1602
02:01:29,020 --> 02:01:31,284
- 不要拖拉绳索  - 明白，备用泵启动
- No trail line...  - Roger that. Backup pump is on.

1603
02:01:31,355 --> 02:01:32,947
好的，我们要升起100英尺
All right, we'll do the hoist at 100 feet.

1604
02:01:33,024 --> 02:01:34,355
明白
Roger that.

1605
02:01:35,393 --> 02:01:38,260
科迪亚克，科迪亚克，6208呼叫
Kodiak Ops, Kodiak Ops, rescue 6028.

1606
02:01:38,329 --> 02:01:41,389
6208，允许行动
Rescue 6028, Kodiak Ops. Go ahead.

1607
02:01:41,799 --> 02:01:44,461
救生员准备完毕，检查完毕
Swimmer's ready. Load-checking swimmer.

1608
02:01:46,237 --> 02:01:49,468
救生员准备出仓
And load check complete. Swimmer's going out the door.

1609
02:01:49,540 --> 02:01:52,771
救生员出仓 救生员在下降
Swimmer's out the door. Swimmer's on his way down.

1610
02:02:07,858 --> 02:02:10,088
海岸警卫队直升机，收到请回话
Coast Guard helo, do you copy?

1611
02:02:11,662 --> 02:02:14,392
海岸警卫队直升机，我是救生员1号
Coast Guard helo, this is Rescue Swimmer One.

1612
02:02:14,465 --> 02:02:15,489
收到请回话
Do you copy?

1613
02:02:15,566 --> 02:02:16,828
向前偏右40度
Forward, right 40.

1614
02:02:16,901 --> 02:02:18,425
向前偏右30度，注意高度
Forward, right 30. Watch your altitude.

1615
02:02:18,502 --> 02:02:19,662
明白
Roger.

1616
02:02:52,036 --> 02:02:54,004
停，绳索摩坏了，绳索摩坏了
Hold. I have a fouled cable. Fouled cable.

1617
02:02:54,071 --> 02:02:55,595
解开绳索
Paying out slack.

1618
02:02:57,108 --> 02:02:59,941
海岸警卫队直升机，我是救生员1号
Coast Guard helo, this is Swimmer Number One!

1619
02:03:00,011 --> 02:03:03,606
我在引擎室 舱室就要被淹没了
I'm in the engine room, and the hold of the boat is filling up!

1620
02:03:03,681 --> 02:03:05,672
- 他在试着解开绳索  - 加油
- He's trying to free the cable.  - Come on.

1621
02:03:10,721 --> 02:03:13,155
好了，绳索已解开，绳索已解开
Okay, cable free. Cable free.

1622
02:03:18,629 --> 02:03:19,721
好样的
Attaboy.

1623
02:03:21,365 --> 02:03:23,731
绳索解开，这里有些磨损
Cable's free, and I got a fray right here.

1624
02:03:23,801 --> 02:03:26,668
还可以用，还可以用 我就就指望它了
It's still good. It's still good. I can use it. It's all we got.

1625
02:03:26,737 --> 02:03:27,726
好的，很好
All right, good.

1626
02:03:27,805 --> 02:03:28,999
向后偏左一些，长官
Go back and left, Captain.

1627
02:03:29,073 --> 02:03:30,472
向后偏左，明白
Back and left. Roger that.

1628
02:03:35,880 --> 02:03:37,006
杰克
Jake.

1629
02:03:50,728 --> 02:03:51,956
加油
Come on.

1630
02:03:52,129 --> 02:03:53,323
加油
Come on.

1631
02:03:55,700 --> 02:03:56,826
杰克
Jake!

1632
02:04:02,373 --> 02:04:03,465
杰克
Jake!

1633
02:04:06,377 --> 02:04:07,401
杰克？
Jake?

1634
02:04:07,478 --> 02:04:10,242
军士长 军士长，是你吗？
Senior? Senior, is that you?

1635
02:04:10,414 --> 02:04:11,779
金鱼
Goldfish!

1636
02:04:11,916 --> 02:04:15,682
门上的锁我都检查过了，就是松不开，卡住了
I checked all the locks on the door. I can't get them loose. They're stuck.

1637
02:04:15,753 --> 02:04:17,812
我知道，我知道是什么问题
l know. l see the problem.

1638
02:04:18,823 --> 02:04:21,053
军士长，马上就淹满了
It's filling up, Senior Chief!

1639
02:04:21,492 --> 02:04:24,256
二级军士长，把我弄出去!
Senior Chief! Get me out of here!

1640
02:04:29,934 --> 02:04:32,334
我几乎被淹没了!你得把门打开!
I'm almost submerged! You gotta get the door open!

1641
02:04:32,403 --> 02:04:33,893
撑住，杰克
Hold on, Jake.

1642
02:04:52,690 --> 02:04:54,817
军士长!船长在那边
Senior! The captain's body!

1643
02:04:55,159 --> 02:04:57,320
我们得放弃他了
We gotta let him go. Come on.

1644
02:05:04,902 --> 02:05:06,392
杰克，他已经死了
Jake, he's gone!

1645
02:05:16,046 --> 02:05:17,138
杰克!
Jake!

1646
02:05:19,650 --> 02:05:21,015
救生员都出来了
I got both swimmers coming out.

1647
02:05:21,085 --> 02:05:23,679
- 两个救生员都能看见  - 好的，我看到他们了
- Both swimmers are in sight.  - All right, I got them.

1648
02:05:41,672 --> 02:05:42,832
钩子已放下
Hook is going down.

1649
02:05:42,907 --> 02:05:46,172
偏右40，钩子下落中
Let's go forward, right 40. Hook is halfway down.

1650
02:05:46,310 --> 02:05:48,073
我们要用钩子连在一起
I'm hooking into you.

1651
02:05:48,145 --> 02:05:50,443
我们只有一次机会
We're only gonna get one shot at this.

1652
02:05:53,350 --> 02:05:54,578
我钩好了
I'm in.

1653
02:05:55,886 --> 02:05:57,080
我也好了
I'm in!

1654
02:06:11,001 --> 02:06:13,401
我还以为你会去钓鱼
I thought you were going fishing.

1655
02:06:13,471 --> 02:06:15,371
那你说这是什么？
What do you call this?

1656
02:06:20,878 --> 02:06:21,970
哇
Whoa.

1657
02:06:24,415 --> 02:06:28,146
绳索要断了，撑住，撑住!
The cable's starting to part! The cable! Hold, hold, hold!

1658
02:06:31,422 --> 02:06:33,549
撑住，快把他们拉上来
Okay, hold right there. Hold. I'm bringing them up.

1659
02:06:33,624 --> 02:06:36,252
我们得解开它
I gotta jam this cable into the drum.

1660
02:06:43,801 --> 02:06:46,429
你在做什么？ 你在做什么？
What are you doing? What are you doing?

1661
02:06:48,806 --> 02:06:50,740
想都不要想
Don't even think about it.

1662
02:06:50,808 --> 02:06:52,935
这支撑不了我们两个
It's not gonna hold us both.

1663
02:06:53,143 --> 02:06:54,303
什么…
What...

1664
02:06:54,645 --> 02:06:57,705
会的，可以的 别干傻事
Yes, it will. Don't! Lt'll hold!

1665
02:07:01,352 --> 02:07:03,377
军士长落下去!
Senior fell. Senior fell!

1666
02:07:05,723 --> 02:07:07,156
杰克拉住他了 杰克拉住他了
Jake's got him. Jake's got him.

1667
02:07:07,224 --> 02:07:08,987
我得把他们拉上来
I gotta get them up.

1668
02:07:30,581 --> 02:07:32,105
我不会放弃的！
I won't let go!

1669
02:07:34,351 --> 02:07:35,511
我知道
I know.

1670
02:07:57,241 --> 02:07:58,731
军士长!
Senior!

1671
02:08:01,178 --> 02:08:02,577
军士长!
Senior!

1672
02:08:04,248 --> 02:08:05,738
放开我!
Lower me down!

1673
02:08:06,750 --> 02:08:08,240
放开我!
Lower me down!

1674
02:08:08,452 --> 02:08:11,046
他掉下去了，掉下去了 朗道要掉到水里去了!
He just fell! He just fell! Randall fell! Hit the water!

1675
02:08:11,121 --> 02:08:12,110
放开我
Lower me down!

1676
02:08:12,189 --> 02:08:14,157
他掉进水里了，被浪头打到了 只看到船的残片
He's in the water. Been hit by a wave, full debris.

1677
02:08:14,224 --> 02:08:15,691
- 放我下去!  - 不行!
- Put me down!  - I can't!

1678
02:08:15,759 --> 02:08:17,920
你得把我放下去!
You gotta lower me down now!

1679
02:08:20,164 --> 02:08:21,791
让我下去!
Get me out of here!

1680
02:08:21,899 --> 02:08:24,265
- 放我下去!  - 不行!
- You gotta lower me down!  - I can't!

1681
02:08:24,335 --> 02:08:25,324
让我跳下去
I'll free-fall!

1682
02:08:25,803 --> 02:08:29,933
你下去就上不来了 我不能损失两个人
If I do, you don't come back. I can't! I can't lose two!

1683
02:08:32,676 --> 02:08:34,473
损失救生员!损失救生员!
Lost swimmer. Lost swimmer.

1684
02:08:34,545 --> 02:08:37,446
他看到绳索快断了 他就放手了
He saw the cable coming apart. He just let go.

1685
02:08:38,148 --> 02:08:39,979
他从80或90的高度掉下去
He was about 80, 90 feet up, sir.

1686
02:08:40,050 --> 02:08:41,642
他没有上来，我没有看到他
He didn't come up. I don't see him.

1687
02:08:41,719 --> 02:08:43,744
打开远光灯
Flash landing hover lights.

1688
02:08:43,921 --> 02:08:45,218
注意无线电
Monitor the radio, sir.

1689
02:08:45,289 --> 02:08:48,656
寻找照明棒，闪光灯，一切东西 他掉在浪头里
Look for flares, strobes, anything. He fell right in the debris.

1690
02:08:49,593 --> 02:08:52,460
损失救生员，损失救生员
Lost swimmer. Lost swimmer.

1691
02:09:03,440 --> 02:09:04,771
海岸警卫队
The Coast Guard conducted

1692
02:09:04,842 --> 02:09:06,639
为一个人做了历史上
one of the largest search-and-rescue missions

1693
02:09:06,710 --> 02:09:08,507
最大规模的搜救行动
for a single man in its history,

1694
02:09:10,481 --> 02:09:14,042
但一直没有找到二级军士长 本・朗道的尸体
but the body of Senior Chief Ben Randall was never found.

1695
02:09:23,460 --> 02:09:25,087
我很抱歉，海伦
I'm sorry, Helen.

1696
02:09:26,397 --> 02:09:27,955
我们尽了最大努力了
