What makes a legend?

1698
02:09:31,969 --> 02:09:34,164
是一个人在活着的时候做了什么？
Is it what someone did when they were alive...

1699
02:09:34,238 --> 02:09:36,206
朗道从来都不太在意这种事情
Randall never was much for this sort of thing.

1700
02:09:36,273 --> 02:09:39,242
或者在他死去还被别人惦记？
Or how they're remembered after they're gone?

1701
02:09:41,345 --> 02:09:43,279
有些人相信
Some people actually believe

1702
02:09:43,347 --> 02:09:46,646
二级军士长游到了阿留申群岛
Senior Chief made the swim to the Aleutian Islands.

1703
02:09:47,584 --> 02:09:50,417
他在某个海滩
He's standing on a distant beach somewhere

1704
02:09:50,521 --> 02:09:52,853
手上拿着钓竿
with a fishing pole in his hand.

1705
02:09:55,993 --> 02:09:58,826
几个星期后我得到了答案
But I found my answer a couple weeks later.

1706
02:10:04,435 --> 02:10:05,800
他在哪儿？
Where is he?

1707
02:10:09,139 --> 02:10:10,970
伙计，那边没有人了
There's nobody else out there, man.

1708
02:10:11,041 --> 02:10:12,633
不，他在那儿
No, he was there.

1709
02:10:13,610 --> 02:10:15,840
他一直在我身边
He was with me the whole time.

1710
02:10:16,013 --> 02:10:18,811
他说他会等到救援到来
He said he would hold on till help arrived.

1711
02:10:19,917 --> 02:10:21,544
他从不放弃
He never let go.

1712
02:10:42,172 --> 02:10:45,801
传说在水下有个传奇人物
There's a legend of a man who lives beneath the sea.

1713
02:10:48,278 --> 02:10:50,143
他是个捞人的
He is a fisher of men,

1714
02:10:51,248 --> 02:10:54,581
给了所有落伍者希望
a last hope for all those who have been left behind.

1715
02:10:58,188 --> 02:11:00,349
他是个守护神
He is known as the Guardian.

1716
02:11:03,327 --> 02:11:06,728
本・朗道总是说生命就是不断地做选择
Ben Randall always said life is about making choices.

1717
02:11:07,264 --> 02:11:11,200
最后，他自己的决断帮我做了决定
In the end, by making his, he helped me make mine.

1718
02:11:11,335 --> 02:11:12,802
什么会让你难忘？
What do you remember?

1719
02:11:12,870 --> 02:11:14,462
你身上的气味是什么样的？ 你看起来怎么样？
What did you smell? What did you see?

1720
02:11:14,538 --> 02:11:16,369
这会让你怎样
How did this make you

1721
02:11:21,211 --> 02:11:22,269
感觉？
feel?

1722
02:11:28,018 --> 02:11:29,645
我马上就回来
I'll be right back.

1723
02:11:34,258 --> 02:11:36,249
你来这里做什么？
What are you doing here?

1724
02:11:38,462 --> 02:11:39,952
我对你撒了谎
I lied to you.

1725
02:11:41,598 --> 02:11:43,190
我做不到临时的
I can't do casual.


